    <item>
      <title>立法者要求司法部调查苹果关闭 iMessage 应用程序的行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/lawmakers-ask-doj-to-probe-apple-for-shuttering-imessage-apps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群两党议员要求司法部调查苹果公司关闭允许 Android 设备使用 iMessage 服务与 iPhone 用户通信的第三方应用程序是否违反了反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/lawmakers-ask-doj-to-probe-apple-for-shuttering-imessage-apps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 15:58:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>专利丢失后苹果将停止在美国销售智能手表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/apple-to-stop-selling-some-apple-watch-models-on-patent-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于专利纠纷，苹果公司将停止在美国销售最新版本的智能手表，并在繁忙的假日季节将部分最畅销的设备撤出市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/apple-to-stop-selling-some-apple-watch-models-on-patent-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 15:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Farfetch 通过 Coupang 提供 5 亿美元贷款寻找救援者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/farfetch-gets-backer-with-500-million-injection-from-coupang</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Farfetch Ltd. 从电子商务公司 Coupang Inc. 那里获得了生命线，Coupang Inc. 同意提供 5 亿美元贷款，购买资产并将这家陷入困境的时尚平台股票退市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/farfetch-gets-backer-with-500-million-injection-from-coupang</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 14:59:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
